appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
If App Crashes Check Permissions
1) Trail - Course Of Movement
2) Number Of Satellites
3) Azimuth
4) Map Bearing - M.B
5) Gps Bearing - GPS.B
6) Cellid / Lac Change On Map - C\L
7) Network Signal Strength On Map - DT
8) Measure Distance Between Two Points - >--< Button
9) Marker Sign On Map - Marker Button
10) Draw Polygon On Map - Polygon Button, Press On Map On Two Points
All Featuers Was Tested On Android 9 - Samsung S9
Google Has Disabled Some Abilities On Android 10 and 11 - Sorry!
